leftDrillDowns.displayName: Run Search on HTTP  User Agent

dashboardQueries.name: 9a479479-ac11-4b3b-a275-1e9a52961cd2
dashboardQueries.query:
metadata.vendor_name="Corelight"
metadata.product_event_type="http"
$host_header=target.hostname
$host_header!=""
$combined_fields=strings.concat(network.session_id, target.ip, principal.ip)
match:
    $host_header
outcome:
    $count=count_distinct($combined_fields)
order:
    $count asc 
limit:
    10

dashboardQueries.name: 2ff9a546-a79c-4ed3-ac48-c6e2de7e4a86
dashboardQueries.query:
metadata.vendor_name="Corelight"
metadata.product_event_type="http"
$local_orig=if(principal.ip in cidr %internal_cidr_list, "true", "false")
$local_resp=if(target.ip in cidr %internal_cidr_list, "true", "false") 
($local_orig="true" AND $local_resp="true") OR ($local_orig="false" AND $local_resp="true")
$user_agent=network.http.user_agent
$user_agent!=""
$combined_fields=strings.concat(network.session_id target.ip, principal.ip)
match:
    $user_agent
outcome:
    $count=count_distinct($combined_fields)
order:
    $count desc

dashboardQueries.name: df60790b-2707-4b5c-be55-f9f5057c2d72
dashboardQueries.query:
metadata.vendor_name="Corelight"
metadata.product_event_type="http"
network.http.method!=""
$host_header=target.hostname
$host_header!=""
$status_code=strings.concat(network.http.response_code, "")
$status_code!=""
$status_msg=about.labels["status_msg"]
$combined_fields=strings.concat(network.session_id, target.ip, principal.ip)
match:
    $host_header, $status_code, $status_msg
outcome:
    $count=count_distinct($combined_fields)
order:
    $count desc
